{"id":107347,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/09/简讯：四名日本人在中国被调查/","date":"2010-09-24T13:45:53Z","modified":"2010-09-25T06:01:40Z","title":"简讯：四名日本人在中国被调查","content":"<div>\n<p>4名日本人在中国被指涉嫌进入军事禁区，非法拍摄军事目标，遭中国当局调查。</p>\n<p>新华社称，这四人擅自进入河北省会石家庄的一个军事禁区。</p>\n<p>国家安全机关接到报告后，即对他们采取措施，并对其问题进行审查。</p>\n<p>这个案件的发生正赶上中日两国关系因钓鱼岛（日本称尖阁列岛）的争执而陷入紧张。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/aIrCK051_30zy1TMsPWCwggoAGU/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/aIrCK051_30zy1TMsPWCwggoAGU/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/aIrCK051_30zy1TMsPWCwggoAGU/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/aIrCK051_30zy1TMsPWCwggoAGU/1/di\"></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=ptjP1PW1iQk:X0J0Z1t7UXI:mqyYa2mfVbY\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=mqyYa2mfVbY\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=ptjP1PW1iQk:X0J0Z1t7UXI:PFx2F_oWK34\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=PFx2F_oWK34\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=ptjP1PW1iQk:X0J0Z1t7UXI:DUWcskeyX7o\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=DUWcskeyX7o\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=ptjP1PW1iQk:X0J0Z1t7UXI:clraHZBW0_I\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=clraHZBW0_I\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=ptjP1PW1iQk:X0J0Z1t7UXI:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=ptjP1PW1iQk:X0J0Z1t7UXI:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/ptjP1PW1iQk\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p>请看原文：<br />\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/china/2010/09/100923_brief_china_japanese.shtml\" title=\"简讯：四名日本人在中国被调查\">简讯：四名日本人在中国被调查</a></p>\n","author":138,"categories":[8779],"tags":[14208]}